        public void createEditPolicies()
        GRAPHICAL_NODE_ROLE Policy must be installed here so that we can make the Compartments unselectable for connection creation, when the user steped in the compartment. The other EditPolicys are installed through calling ORMTypeEditPart.createEditPolicies().
